't have a printer.">model</button></li><li class="practice-item"><span class="practice-num">06</span><span class="practice-q"><span class="drop-slot" data-drop data-expected="Mia doesn't have">drop</span> many documents on the table.</span><button class="practice-hint" data-answer="Mia doesn't have many documents on the table.">model</button></li><li class="practice-item"><span class="practice-num">07</span><span class="practice-q"><span class="drop-slot" data-drop data-expected="Do you have">drop</span> a pencil?</span><button class="practice-hint" data-answer="Do you have a pencil?">model</button></li><li class="practice-item"><span class="practice-num">08</span><span class="practice-q"><span class="drop-slot" data-drop data-expected="Does Alex have">drop</span> a lamp?</span><button class="practice-hint" data-answer="Does Alex have a lamp?">model</button></li></ol><div class="block-nav"><a class="btn primary" href="#text">Next: reading</a></div></section>

