    <section class="block" id="text"><header class="block-head"><div class="block-num">07</div><div class="block-title-wrap"><div class="block-kicker">Listening / Reading</div><h2 class="block-title">Alex and Mia's things</h2></div><div class="block-time">≈ 7 min</div></header><div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;"><button class="btn ghost" id="listenBtn">Listen</button><button class="btn ghost" id="showTextBtn">Show text</button></div><div class="text-card" id="readingCard" style="display: block;"><h3>Alex and Mia's things</h3><p id="readingScript" data-kids="Alex has a small room. He has a bed near the window. He has a desk next to the bed. On the desk, he has two books, a blue notebook, and some pencils. Alex has a lamp on the desk. He has a football on the floor. He doesn't have a TV in his room. He doesn't have many toys on the floor. Alex likes his room because it is clean and bright." data-adults="Mia has a small workspace at home. She has a desk near the window. On the desk, she has a laptop, two notebooks, and some pens. She has a lamp and a small plant. Mia has a coffee mug near the laptop. She doesn't have a printer in the room. She doesn't have many documents on the table. Mia likes her workspace because it is quiet and simple.">Alex has a small room. He has a bed near the window. He has a desk next to the bed. On the desk, he has two books, a blue notebook, and some pencils. Alex has a lamp on the desk. He has a football on the floor. He doesn't have a TV in his room. He doesn't have many toys on the floor. Alex likes his room because it is clean and bright.</p></div><ol class="practice-list"><li class="practice-item"><span class="practice-num">01</span><span class="practice-q">Does Alex (Mia) have a small room / workspace? <span class="choice-row"><button class="choice" data-correct="true">Yes</button><button class="choice">No</button></span></span><button class="practice-hint" data-answer="Yes, he/she does.">hint</button></li><li class="practice-item"><span class="practice-num">02</span><span class="practice-q">Does Alex (Mia) have a desk near the window? <span class="choice-row"><button class="choice" data-correct="true">Yes</button><button class="choice">No</button></span></span><button class="practice-hint" data-answer="Yes.">hint</button></li><li class="practice-item"><span class="practice-num">03</span><span class="practice-q">Does Alex (Mia) have two books / two notebooks? <span class="choice-row"><button class="choice" data-correct="true">Yes</button><button class="choice">No</button></span></span><button class="practice-hint" data-answer="Yes.">hint</button></li><li class="practice-item"><span class="practice-num">04</span><span class="practice-q">Does Alex (Mia) have a lamp? <span class="choice-row"><button class="choice" data-correct="true">Yes</button><button class="choice">No</button></span></span><button class="practice-hint" data-answer="Yes.">hint</button></li><li class="practice-item"><span class="practice-num">05</span><span class="practice-q">Does Alex (Mia) have a TV / a printer? <span class="choice-row"><button class="choice">Yes</button><button class="choice" data-correct="true">No</button></span></span><button class="practice-hint" data-answer="No.">hint</button></li><li class="practice-item"><span class="practice-num">06</span><span class="practice-q">Does Alex (Mia) have many toys / many documents on the floor/table? <span class="choice-row"><button class="choice">Yes</button><button class="choice" data-correct="true">No</button></span></span><button class="practice-hint" data-answer="No.">hint</button></li><li class="practice-item"><span class="practice-num">07</span><span class="practice-q">Does Alex have a football? / Does Mia have a coffee mug? <span class="choice-row"><button class="choice" data-correct="true">Yes</button><button class="choice">No</button></span></span><button class="practice-hint" data-answer="Yes.">hint</button></li><li class="practice-item"><s